        "description": {
          "type": "description",
          "settings": {
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 24
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_xFUnQz": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Most Frequently Asked Questions",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Q: What should I do if the mask doesn’t stick well?</strong></p><p><strong>A:</strong> For best adherence, we recommend applying the mask to freshly cleansed, slightly damp skin. Take a moment to smooth it out gently, pressing down around the contours of your face. If needed, you can lay back and relax while it works its magic — the extra time also allows for deeper absorption. Some slip is natural due to the serum-rich formula, but that’s part of what makes it so effective at delivering moisture.</p><p><strong>Q: What ingredients are in this?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>Our Bio-Collagen Mask is formulated with skin-supportive ingredients designed to deliver deep hydration and visible firmness. Key ingredients include:</p><ul><li><strong>Hydrolyzed fish collagen (from salmon)</strong> – known for its smaller molecular size, making it easier for the skin to absorb. It helps support elasticity, smoothness, and firmness, especially in aging or dehydrated skin.<br/></li><li><strong>Niacinamide</strong> – helps brighten skin and even out tone.<br/></li><li><strong>Hyaluronic acid</strong> – provides intense, long-lasting hydration and plumping.<br/></li><li><strong>Peptides</strong> – support collagen production and improve overall skin resilience.<br/></li></ul><p>The mask’s <strong>hydrogel base</strong> allows for slow-release absorption, helping the skin drink in every ingredient — not just sit on the surface.</p><p><strong>Q: Is this vegan and cruelty-free?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>We’re proud to say our mask is <strong>cruelty-free</strong> — absolutely no animal testing is involved at any stage of formulation or production.</p><p>While it does contain <strong>hydrolyzed collagen</strong>, which is not plant-derived, we source it responsibly from marine ingredients. We know terms like “vegan collagen” can be confusing — and while some plant-based ingredients can help support collagen production, <strong>true collagen itself can only come from fish-based sources.</strong></p><p>That said, we’re always exploring more sustainable innovations while staying committed to delivering results — and kindness — through skincare.</p><p><strong>Q:  Do I need to sit still for 3–4 hours to get the best results?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>Not at all! The mask is designed to move with you — most of our customers wear it while winding down for the night, whether that’s reading, watching TV, or getting ready for bed.</p><p>In fact, <strong>78% of users wear the mask while they sleep</strong>, and many report <strong>up to 24% better hydration and visible skin smoothness</strong> when used overnight. The longer it stays on, the more time your skin has to soak in the benefits — all while you rest.</p><p><strong>Q: Doesn’t collagen come from within? How can this penetrate the skin?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>You’re absolutely right — collagen is produced naturally in the body, but production slows with age. Our mask uses <strong>hydrolyzed marine collagen</strong>, which is broken down into smaller peptides that are better able to <strong>absorb into the upper layers of the skin</strong>. It’s not about replacing collagen deep inside — it’s about supporting the skin’s structure, hydration, and visible bounce from the outside in.</p><p><strong>Q: How long do the effects last after using the mask?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>You’ll typically notice <strong>immediate hydration and visible plumpness</strong> right after use. With weekly application, many customers see more long-term improvements in firmness and glow. Think of it as part of your ongoing skincare ritual, not just a one-time fix.</p><p><strong>Q: Can the same mask be used more than once?</strong></p><p><strong>A: </strong>We don’t recommend reusing the mask. It’s designed as a <strong>single-use treatment</strong> to maintain hygiene and ensure maximum potency of the ingredients. Once used, the mask has already released most of its actives into your skin.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_ChWQiJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does collagen mouth tape actually work?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>It gently keeps your lips closed during sleep, training your body to breathe through your nose.</p><p>This increases oxygen flow, reduces puffiness, hydrates skin, and promotes collagen production, all while sculpting your jawline overnight.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 12,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QnkEdx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How quickly will I see results?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Most users notice benefits within the first 3-5 nights of consistent use</strong>, including better nose breathing, less dry mouth, and smoother, more hydrated lips in the morning.</p><p><strong>With consistent nightly use for 2–3 weeks</strong>, many women report a more relaxed jaw position and a subtly more sculpted-looking jawline.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 12,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8h6X4m": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if I have allergies or my sinuses are blocked?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Many women with allergies find mouth taping feels more comfortable over time, as nose breathing helps filter and humidify the air.<br/><br/>If you have mild congestion, the breathing hole helps you stay comfortable. If congestion feels heavy, simply skip use until it clears.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwzWVt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Will this work with my CPAP machine?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Many customers use the collagen mouth tape alongside their CPAP without issues, and some find it helps reduce mouth leaks.<br/><br/>If you have sleep apnea or use CPAP therapy, we recommend checking with your sleep specialist before use.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does this help with sleep apnea?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>It depends on the type. If you have obstructive sleep apnea (OSA), always speak with your doctor first — mouth tape is not a treatment replacement.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is it safe? Can I suffocate?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes. The beginner-friendly pinhole allows airflow and speech if needed, so your lips aren’t fully sealed. It gently encourages nasal breathing with no risk of suffocation.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-6 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p><p><strong>Returns:<br/></strong>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! If you are not completely happy with your order, we accept returns and exchanges within 60 days from the date of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us via the website or via email: info@niforashop.com</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
