            "title_highlight_color": "#8b1638",
            "text": "<p>Sleeping with your mouth open can lead to dryness, dehydration, and that “cotton-mouth” feeling when you wake up. By encouraging lip closure and nose breathing, <strong>our tape helps maintain oral moisture, reduces dryness, and diminishes morning throat and mouth irritation</strong> — leaving you feeling fresher and more comfortable.</p>",
