        },
        "row_nnbML9": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/8_a614f1f9-5a86-408d-bf65-bd42218d50d6.png",
            "caption": "",
            "title": "<strong>Better Sleep & Better Rest,</strong> Naturally",
            "title_highlight_color": "#8b1638",
            "text": "<p>Our Collagen Mouth Tape <strong>gently supports natural nose breathing</strong>, helping your body settle into deeper, calmer sleep without effort. By keeping the lips softly closed, it <strong>reduces dry mouth</strong>, <strong>minimizes snoring</strong>, and <strong>encourages better oxygen flow throughout the night</strong>. The result? You wake up feeling more refreshed, restored, and hydrated — all from a simple nightly ritual that works with your body, not against it.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
